#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4437
msgid "Rules of the game"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4439
msgid "InfectionClass is a team game between humans and the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4441
msgid "All players start as a human."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4443
msgid "10 seconds later, a few players become infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4445
msgid "The goal for the humans is to survive until the army cleans the map."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4447
msgid "The goal for the infected is to infect all humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4449
msgid "See also `/help pages`"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4454
msgid "How to translate the mod"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4456
msgid "Create an account on Crowdin and join the translation team:"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4463
msgid "White hole"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4465
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "White hole pulls the infected into its center."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4469
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "Receive it by killing at least {int:NumKills} infected as a Scientist."
msgid_plural ""
"Receive it by killing at least {int:NumKills} of the infected as a Scientist."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4473
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "Use the laser rifle to place it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4478
msgid "Targeted chat messages"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4481
msgid ""
"Use “/w <PlayerName> <My Message>” to send a private message to this player."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4483
msgid ""
"Use “/msg !<ClassName> <My Message>” to send a private message to all "
"players with a specific class."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4485
msgid "Example: “/msg !medic I'm wounded!”"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4487
msgid "Use “/msg !near” to send a private message to all players near you."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4492
msgid "Persistent player mute"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4495
msgid "Use “/mute <PlayerName>” to mute this player."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4497
msgid ""
"Unlike a client mute this will persist between map changes and wears off "
"when either you or the muted player disconnects."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4499
msgid "Example: “/mute nameless tee”"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4505
msgid "How to use taxi mode"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4507
msgid "Two or more humans can form a taxi."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4509
msgid ""
"In order to use it, both humans have to disable hook protection (usually, "
"with F3). The human being hooked becomes the driver."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4511
msgid ""
"To get off the taxi, jump. To drop off your passengers, enable hook "
"protection (usually, with F3)."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4516
msgid "Fast round"
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4519
msgid ""
"In the fast rounds *more* humans become infected initially, the spawning "
"rate is increased and the round time limit is decreased. White hole is also "
"disabled."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4588
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid "The Mercenary can fly in the air using their machine gun."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4589
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"They can also create a powerful bomb with their hammer that can be charged "
"by hitting it or with a laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4593
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} "
"damage point and prevent the infected from healing."
msgid_plural ""
"Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} "
"damage points and prevent the infected from healing."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4601
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "The Medic can protect humans with the hammer by giving them armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4602
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid ""
"Grenades with medicine give armor to everybody in their range, including "
"Heroes and the Medic themself."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4607
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Tranqulizer rifle makes the infected fall asleep for {sec:Duration}."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4611
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Laser rifle revives the infected, but at the cost of 17 hp and armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4613
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Medic also has a powerful shotgun that can knock back the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4616
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The Hero has all standard weapons."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4617
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The Hero has to find a flag only visible to them. Stand still to be pointed "
"towards it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4618
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The flag gifts a health point, {int:NumArmorGift} armor and full ammo to all "
"humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4620
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"It fully heals the Hero and it can grant a turret which you can place down "
"with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4621
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The gift to all humans is only applied when the flag is surrounded by hearts "
"and armor."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4622
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid ""
"The Hero cannot be healed by a Medic, but it can withstand a hit from an "
"infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4625
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "The Engineer can build walls with the hammer to block the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4626
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "When an infected touches the wall, it dies."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4627
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid ""
"The lifespan of a wall is {sec:LifeSpan}, and walls are limited to one per "
"player at the same time."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4632
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "The Soldier creates floating bombs with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4635
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} time."
msgid_plural "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} times."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4639
msgid "Use the hammer to place the bomb and explode it multiple times."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4642
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid ""
"The Ninja can throw flash grenades that can freeze the infected for three "
"seconds."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4647
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid ""
"Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash "
"{int:NinjaJump} time before touching the ground."
msgid_plural ""
"Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash "
"{int:NinjaJump} times before touching the ground."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4652
msgid ""
"They also have a laser rifle that blinds the target for a short period of "
"time."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4653
msgid ""
"Ninja gets special targets. For killing a target, extra points and abilities "
"are awarded."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4657
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid ""
"The Sniper can lock the position in mid-air for 15 seconds with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4659
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid ""
"The locked position increases the Sniper's rifle damage from usual 10-13 to "
"30 damage points."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4661
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4664
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "The Scientist can pose floating mines with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4667
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgid_plural "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4670
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Scientist has also grenades that teleport them."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4671
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid ""
"A lucky Scientist devoted to killing can get a white hole that sucks the "
"infected in which can be placed with the laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4675
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid ""
"The Biologist has a shotgun with bouncing bullets and can create a spring "
"laser trap by shooting with the laser rifle."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4677
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid ""
"They are also immune to continuous poison effect, and can stop it on "
"teammates with the Hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4681
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid ""
"The Looper has a laser wall that slows down the infected and a low-range "
"laser rifle with a high fire rate."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4683
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4686
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid ""
"Smoker has a powerful hook that hurts humans and sucks their blood, "
"restoring the Smoker's health."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4688
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid "It can also infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4691
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "The Boomer explodes when it attacks."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4692
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "All humans affected by the explosion become infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4693
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4696
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid ""
"The Hunter can jump two times in the air and has some resistance to knock-"
"backs."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4698
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4699
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4702
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Bat can jump endlessly in the air but it cannot infect humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4703
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Instead, it can hammer humans to steal their health and heal itself."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4704
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "The hammer is also useful for healing the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4705
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4708
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid ""
"The Ghost is invisible until a human comes nearby, it takes damage, or it "
"uses the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4710
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4711
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4714
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid ""
"The Spider has a web hook that automatically grabs any human touching it."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4715
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid "The web hook mode can be toggled by switching the weapon."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4716
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid ""
"In both modes the hook inflicts 1 damage point per second and can grab a "
"human for longer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4720
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid ""
"The Ghoul can devour anything that has died nearby, which makes it stronger, "
"faster and more resistant."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4722
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid ""
"It digests the fodder over time, going back to the normal state. Some "
"nourishment is also lost on death."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4724
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "Ghoul can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4725
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4728
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid ""
"The Slug can make the ground and walls toxic by spreading slime with the "
"hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4729
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "The slime heals the infected and deals damage to humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4730
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "Slug can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4731
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4734
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid ""
"The Voodoo does not die immediately when killed but instead enters Spirit "
"mode for a short time."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4736
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid ""
"While in Spirit mode it cannot be killed. When the time is up it finally "
"dies."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4737
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "Voodoo can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4738
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4741
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "The Witch can provide a spawn point for the infected."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4742
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "If the Witch dies, it disappears and is replaced by another class."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4743
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "Witch can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4744
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4747
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "The Undead cannot die. Instead of dying, it gets frozen for 10 seconds."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4748
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "If an infected heals it, the freeze effect disappears."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4749
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "Undead can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr ""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4750
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr ""

